Class ServicePanelFactoryImpl

java.lang.Object
  gr.interamerican.wicket.bo2.factories.ServicePanelFactoryImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ServicePanelFactory
public class ServicePanelFactoryImpl
extends Object
implements ServicePanelFactory

Implementation of ServicePanelFactory. This Factory expects to find a key with name pathToDefaultPanelFactoryDefinition in the Bo2 deployment parameters file. The key's value is a file that contains the resource path of all properties files that declare associations of panelIds and ServicePanel implementation classes.
